text: Ricardo Adams (born 23 October 1994) is a Guyanese cricketer. He made his List A debut for Guyana in the 2017–18 Regional Super50 on 12 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Guyanese cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Guyana cricketers
